    "title": "Lead Investment Banker at HDFC Securities",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Investment Banker with drive and ambition, HDFC Securities in Indore is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout HDFC Securities:\nHDFC Securities is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with HDFC Securities!",
